2010-09-08: gWaei 3.1.0
  The program had its backend rewritten to be more object oriented and modular.
  The program uses about 1/3 less memory on startup and less CPU when idle.  The 
  search toolbar now uses the primary toolbar style when the other toolbar is not
  shown.  The searches now feature a widget that opens a contextual menu for 
  searching for the word in another dictionary or online.
